											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="On &quot;Present your weapon, soldier,&quot; She abruptly turns to the player and points an accusing finger. As she moves and points she steps forward. Magical hands appear around her wrists, arms, and shoulders, showing the player how she is bound. If she moves too far, she'll be pulled back by her arms. She looks down at the hands and grimaces in rage, stepping back into place as the hands fade: &quot;Plunge it into the Nightsong. I cannot stop you. But know this. Slams chest again, fury in her movements." />
